00:08:53.480 --> 00:08:58.199
All right. We've got 10 minutes with you. So please leave a little bit of time for questions.

76
00:08:58.199 --> 00:09:04.439
Thank you. Thank you. Good morning. So yes, I'm Jacob Perry, appearing with me as Mr Lloyd Gallagher.

77
00:09:05.319 --> 00:09:09.879
We're appearing on behalf of the Law Association's Technology and Law Committee.

78
00:09:09.879 --> 00:09:12.919
